<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
#parse("include.vm")
<title>Calculations | Webgama</title>
</head>
<body>
	<div id="wrapper">
		#parse("header.vm")
		<div id="container">
			<div class="nav_menu">
				<ul>
					<li><a href="#springUrl("/overview")">Overview</a></li>
					<li><a href="#springUrl("/adjustment")">#springMessage("adjustment.navbar")</a></li>
					<li><a class="active" href="#springUrl("/calculations")">Calculations</a></li>
					<li><a href="#springUrl("/import/xml")">Import</a></li>
					<li><a href="#springUrl("/export")">Export</a></li>
				</ul>
			</div>
			<div id="content">
				<div class="panel_header">
					<h2>Calculations</h2>
				</div>
				<div id="calculations">
					<div id="my_calculations">
						My Calculations #if ($myCalculations.isEmpty())
						<p>
							<i>No calculations added yet</i>
						</p>
						#else
						<div class="accordion">
							#foreach ($input in $myCalculations)
							<h3>
								$input.name <span class="time">$dateTool.format("yyyy-MM-dd
									HH:mm:ss",$input.time.toDate())</span>
							</h3>
							<div class="accor_content">
								<a href="#springUrl("/adjustment/onepage/${input.id}")">Edit in One page</a>
							</div>
							#end
						</div>
						#end
					</div>
					<div id="shared_calculations">
						Shared Calculations #if ($sharedCalculations.isEmpty())
						<p>
							<i>No calculations added yet</i>
						</p>
						#else
						<div class="accordion">
							#foreach ($input in $sharedCalculations)
							<h3>
								$input.name <span class="time">$dateTool.format("yyyy-MM-dd
									HH:mm:ss",$input.time.toDate())</span>
							</h3>
							<div class="accor_content">
								<p>Cras dictum. Pellentesque habitant morbi tristique
									senectus et netus et malesuada fames ac turpis egestas.
									Vestibulum ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et
									ultrices posuere cubilia Curae; Aenean lacinia mauris vel est.</p>
							</div>
							#end
						</div>
						#end
					</div>
				</div>
				<div id="quick_links">
				<ul>
				<li><a href="#springUrl("/overview")">Index</a></li>
				<li><a href="#springUrl("/import/xml")">Import</a></li>
				</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	#parse("footer.vm")
</body>
</html>